   RowBox[{
   "Print", "[", "\"\<\!\(\*SubscriptBox[\(R\), \(11\)]\) and \
\!\(\*SubscriptBox[\(R\), \(22\)]\) have become identities, and we can \
\!\(\*StyleBox[\"algebraically\",FontSlant->\"Italic\"]\) solve \
