is possible we may obtain an alternate solution by setting \
A(t,r)=\\!\\(\\*SuperscriptBox[\\(c\\), \\(2\\)]\\) \
\\!\\(\\*StyleBox[\\\"before\\\",FontSlant->\\\"Italic\\\"]\\) solving the \
